{"id":477967,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":23}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"毛主席是我们心中的最红最红的太阳　毛泽东思想是我们革命的最亮最亮的灯塔","genre":"","count":"215","ytitle":"","mtitle":"上海全城齐欢腾","ftitle":"","authors":["胡永槐"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海汽轮机厂　胡永槐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浦江滚滚笑出声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗满天如彩云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福喜讯北京来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海全城齐欢腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢炉旁听喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁工人添虎劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝令平炉吐红浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里江山钢铸成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰产田里听喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社社员喜盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头底下涌棉粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收捷报飞北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练兵场上听喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵个个表决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当兵要当“红卫兵”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世世代代掌红印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福喜讯北京来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海全城齐欢腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风雷向前进!"}]}